headline: Should Omvoh’s Clinical Results and Innovation Drive a Rethink of Eli Lilly’s (LLY) Specialty Focus?
summary: In recent days, Eli Lilly announced new long-term clinical data for Omvoh showing sustained efficacy and safety in ulcerative colitis, while also strengthening its leadership in obesity and diabetes treatments with continued strong performance from Mounjaro and Zepbound. The company's active recruitment of high-profile former FDA leaders and progress in expanding digital health initiatives further highlight its ongoing focus on innovation and regulatory expertise.
